india trade deficit fall india 's trade deficit is provision estim at 58.34 billion rupe in the first 10 month of fiscal 1986/87 end march , compar with 70.62 billion in the year ago period , the commerc ministri said . export rose in the latest period to 100.75 billion rupe from the a year earlier 86.09 billion and import to 159.09 billion from 156.71 billion in the period , the figur show . the trade deficit for all of 1986/87 is provision estim at around 70 billion rupe from an estim record 87.47 billion in 1985/86 and actual 53.18 billion in 1984/85 , commerc minist p. shiv shanker told report last month .